
BONUS.ASH.1.12.98

The following are all considered "bonuses" :

* set_no_steal_flag(1);   makes an item theft proof, very handy.
* set_light(1);           this item will (glow) lighting up a room.
* adj_enchant(x);         maximum +5 with or w/o with enchant spell
* set_opb(x);             bonus to offense
* set_dpb(x);             bonus to defense
* set_spb(x);             bonus to stealth 
* set_cpb(x);             bonus to casting
* set_protection(spell)   immunity to a spell (needs ash's approval)




